 class=\"tag\">AI agents</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"item-title\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47300329\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ask HN: Please restrict new accounts from posting (AI-generated posts concern)</a>\n                    <span class=\"source-badge type-discussion\">HN</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item-description\">Community discussion about the rise of AI-generated posts on Hacker News, particularly from new accounts, and potential solutions to maintain content quality and prevent bot spam.</div>\n                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                    <span class=\"date\">2026-03-08</span>\n                    <span class=\"tag\">AI content</span>\n                    <span class=\"tag\">platform moderation</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"item-title\">\n                    <a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/08/will-the-pentagons-anthropic-controversy-scare-startups-away-from-defense-work/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Will the Pentagon's Anthropic controversy scare startups away from defense work?</a>\n                    <span class=\"source-badge type-opinion\">TechCrunch</span>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item-description\">Discussion about the controversy surrounding Anthropic's Pentagon deal and its potential impact on AI startups considering defense contracts.</div>\n                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n                    <span class=\"date\">2026-03-08</span>\n                    <span class=\"tag\">Anthropic</span>\n                    <span class=\"tag\">AI ethics</span>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"item\">\n                <div class=\"item-title\">\n                    <a href=\"https://techcru